title: Defqon.1 Weekend Festival 2014 Radio Rip
description:
Defqon.1 Weekend Festival 2014 Radio Rip

This is a radio rip from q-dance radio, the quality is their fault, not mine. ;)
Open Defqon.1 Weekend Festival 2014.m3u in your player if you want to listen to the sets in order.

The sets are the full sets as broadcasted. But note that not all sets were broadcasted in their full form.
Hopefully I've cut everything properly, it's over 60 hours of content, so it's very plausible that I missed something,
especially these late night/early morning sets where they just seem to get on/off as they like without saying anything.

Unfortunately, Coones saturday set and Actis set got lost in the void. All the others should be intact. There's also ~30 minutes before the opening.


Enjoy!
